snippet.title: Le Périple d'un Sauvaginier 2 - La bande annonce officielle - ( Romain Chasse Passion )
snippet.description:
✨ Le Périple d’un Sauvaginier 2 ✨

Le Sud-Est… des paysages incroyables, des rencontres inoubliables, des instants gravés à jamais.
Ce voyage m’a encore une fois prouvé que la chasse, la nature et les liens humains vont bien au-delà d’une simple passion.

Mais ce soir, ce n’est pas encore l’heure de tout vous dévoiler…
À 19h, vous découvrez la bande-annonce officielle 🎬

⚠️ Le film complet ne sortira pas aujourd’hui comme certains l’espéraient… Il faudra patienter un peu plus.
📅 Rendez-vous le 30/09/2025 à 19h pour la sortie du film.

Parce qu’un tel périple, ça se savoure, et ça se mérite. 🔥

snippet.title: Among Us: New Viper Role Trailer 🐍
snippet.description:
YOOO IT'S AN UPDATE AND IT'S OUT NOW. It's the Viper! Use your Acid ability and watch the Crewmate's body slowly melt away. No evidence of any crime? No reason to call an Emergency Meeting.

Read more about the role here in update 17.0: https://www.innersloth.com/new-roles-are-on-the-scene-of-17-0-0-emergency-meeting-41/

Among Us is a game of teamwork and betrayal for 4-15 players...in space! Play online or via local WiFi as you attempt to prepare your spaceship for departure, but beware as one or more random players among the Crew are Impostors bent on killing everyone. snippet.title: Katy Perry - The One That Got Away (Lyrics) "in another life i would be your girl"
snippet.description:
Katy Perry - The One That Got Away (Lyrics) "in another life i would be your girl"

Follow Katy Perry:
http://katy.to/InstagramYD
http://katy.to/TikTokYD
http://katy.to/FacebookYD

Lyrics:

[Verse 1]
Summer after high school, when we first met
We'd make out in your Mustang to Radiohead
And on my eighteenth birthday, we got matching tattoos
Used to steal your parents' liquor and climb to the roof
Talked about our future like we had a clue
Never planned that one day, I'd be losing you

[Chorus]
In another life
I would be your girl
We'd keep all our promises
Be us against the world
In another life
I would make you stay
So I don't have to say you were
The one that got away
The one that got away

[Verse 2]
I was June, and you were my Johnny Cash
Never one without the other, we made a pact
Sometimes when I miss you, I put those records on, woah
Someone said you had your tattoo removed
Saw you downtown, singing the blues
It's time to face the music, I'm no longer your muse

[Chorus]
But in another life
I would be your girl
We'd keep all our promises
Be us against the world
In another life
I would make you stay
So I don't have to say you were
The one that got away
The one that got away

[Post-Chorus]
The one
The one
The one
The one that got away

[Bridge]
All this money can't buy me a time machine, no
Can't replace you with a million rings, no
I should've told you what you meant to me, woah
'Cause now I pay the price

[Chorus]
In another life
I would be your girl
We'd keep all our promises
Be us against the world
In another life
I would make you stay
So I don't have to say you were
The one that got away
The one that got away (The one that got away)

[Post-Chorus]
The one (The one)
The one (The one)
The one (The one)
In another life
I would make you stay
So I don't have to say you were
The one that got away
The one that got away
